Subject: Re: [VB] questions about a bus find

I believe crown made those kits,they no longer make
them or are out of business..if I am not mistaken 
corvair engines run backwards requireing the ring and 
pinion to be reversed or you will end up with 4
reverse gears..so be leary about using that trans in
another vw powered bus..

-cameron
